description: The Town that Thread Built Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Phyllis Logan, published by BBC in 2017 - English narration. http://docuwiki.net/images/9/92/The-Town-that-Thread-Built-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ Paisley, Scotland's biggest town, was one of its wealthiest when local mill owners J & P Coats were at the peak of their powers and one of the world's three biggest companies. Narrated by leading actress and one-time 'mill girl' Phyllis Logan.
